high_descs: Turn right and head towards the counter to the right of the fridge.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn around and head towards the kitchen island.
Cut the tomato on the island into several slices.
Turn around and walk towards the fridge on the left side.
Place the knife next to the apple in the fridge.
Turn around and head back towards the kitchen island.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the counter.
Turn around and walk towards the fridge on the left side.
Place the tomato in the fridge, let it cool, and take it back out.
Turn right and walk towards the microwave at the end of the counter.
Place the tomato inside the microwave and close it.
anns.task_desc: Place a cool slice of tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the door, turn left and walk towards the stove, turn left.
Pick up the knife on the counter underneath the lettuce.
Turn all the way around and walk towards the wall, turn right towards the table.
Take the knife and cut up the tomato into slices.
Take the knife, turn right and walk towards the stove, turn left and walk towards the refrigerator, then turn right.
Open the refrigerator and place the knife next to the yellow apple by the black cup then close the door.
Turn right and walk towards the stove, then turn right and walk towards the wall, then turn right towards the table.
Pick up a tomato slice from the table.
Turn right and walk towards the stove, turn right and walk towards the refrigerator, then turn right.
Open the refrigerator and place the slice of tomato behind the knife on the shelf on the left side of the yellow apple, then close the door.
Open the door and pick up the tomato slice then close the door. Turn right and walk towards the stove, turn right then walk towards the wall, then turn left towards the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the tomato slice in front of the gold bowl next to the potato then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of tomato inside of a microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the kitchen door, hang a right, and go to the counter top directly to the right of the refrigerator.
Pick up the knife that is under the head of lettuce.
Turn around and walk to the left end of the kitchen island.
Slice the tomato located in the middle of the counter top of the kitchen island.
Turn around and carry the knife to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator door and place the knife on the shelf directly above the two crisper drawers and in front of the yellow apple, then close the refrigerator door.
Turn around and walk to the left end of the kitchen island.
Pick up a slice from the right side of the tomato as you are facing it.
Turn around and carry the tomato slice to the refrigerator and open the refrigerator door.

Place the tomato slice on the shelf directly above the two crisper drawers and behind the blade end of the knife and to the left of the yellow apple, close the door; open the refrigerator door and pick up the tomato slice.
Turn around and walk to the microwave oven on the counter top across from the left end of the kitchen island.
Open the microwave oven door, place the tomato slice on the left side of the plate in front of the brown bowl, close the oven door.
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato, refrigerate it, then microwave it

high_descs: Back up, turn to the the right and walk around the island, veering to the right at the end near the refrigerator, and walk to the counter directly to the left of the refrigerator.
Pick up the knife by the lettuce from the counter.
Turn around to the left and walk to the island with knife in hand.
Turn right, walking closer to the island.
Turn to the right and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and place the knife on the shelf with the apple and mug.
Close the refrigerator, turn to the right and walk back to the island where the pan is located.
Pick up a slice of the tomato and place it on the counter in front of you
Turn to the right and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, place the tomato slice on the shelf beside the apple, close the refrigerator. Open the refrigerator and remove the tomato.
Turn to the right and walk to the microwave at the end of the counter.
Place the tomato slice into the microwave to the left of the egg. Close the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Placing a cooled tomato slice into a microwave.

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk to the stove.
Turn to the countertop immediately to the left of the stove.
Pick up the knife that is under the head of lettuce, turn around and carry the knife to the end of the kitchen island with the pan on it.
Slice the tomato in the center of the top of the kitchen island.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the knife on the shelf immediately above the crisper drawers and in front of the yellowtheapple.
Close the fridge door, turn to your right and walk to the end of the kitchen island with a pan on it.
Pick up a slice of the tomato and place it directly in front of you.
Pick up the tomato slice and carry it to the fridge.

Open the fridge door and place the tomato slice on the shelf immediately above the crisper drawers at the cutting end of the knife and to the left of the yellow apple, close the fridge door; after cooling open the fridge door, pick up the tomato slice and close the fridge door.
Turn to your right and walk to the microwave oven on the counter across from the island.
Open the microwave door, place the tomato slice on the plate in the microwave in front of the brown bowl, close the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato, refrigerate a slice, heat the slice in the microwave
